setPickingBitmap

public T setPickingBitmap(android.graphics.Bitmap pickingBitmap)
Set marker bitmap for picking. Note: only alpha channel of the bitmap is used, pixels with alpha < 0.5 are considered fully transparent and pixels with >= 0.5 are considered fully opaque. Usually normal marker bitmap can be used as a picking bitmap. By default, fully opaque bitmap is used for picking.

Parameters:
pickingBitmap - marker bitmap for picking
Returns:
builder instance.

setPickingSize

public T setPickingSize(float size)
Set marker size for picking (for detecting clicks on markers). Picking size should be at least as large as size in most cases.

size - relative picking size. Default value is equal to size.
